      "text": [
        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"يَكُونُ بَيْنَ اَلْبِئْرَيْنِ إِنْ كَانَتْ أَرْضاً صُلْبَةً خَمْسُمِائَةِ ذِرَاعٍ وَ إِنْ كَانَتْ رِخْوَةً فَأَلْفُ ذِرَاعٍ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3422 - Imam (as) said: \"There should be a distance of five hundred cubits between two wells if the land is solid, and one thousand cubits if the land is loose.\""
        ]
      }
    },
